1
00:00:48,500 --> 00:00:52,620
=Endless Love=

2
00:00:52,660 --> 00:00:55,580
=Episode 15=

3
00:00:59,520 --> 00:01:00,399
Stop right there!

4
00:01:00,840 --> 00:01:01,640
You slave trader,

5
00:01:01,799 --> 00:01:02,240
you really think

6
00:01:02,479 --> 00:01:03,960
I'd just wait for you to catch me?

7
00:01:07,280 --> 00:01:08,239
So you're all here.

8
00:01:09,519 --> 00:01:10,280
Get lost!

9
00:01:10,560 --> 00:01:12,519
You deceitful hypocrite!

10
00:01:17,799 --> 00:01:18,920
This remedy is for Liu Rushi.

11
00:01:19,079 --> 00:01:20,319
I brought some for you too.

12
00:01:21,799 --> 00:01:23,439
Your Highness is of noble status.

13
00:01:23,680 --> 00:01:25,519
I am but a lowly woman.

14
00:01:25,519 --> 00:01:26,959
It would be improper for us to meet.

15
00:01:27,719 --> 00:01:28,920
Since I have the remedy now,

16
00:01:29,239 --> 00:01:30,000
I'll take my leave.

17
00:01:31,719 --> 00:01:32,760
You're still blaming me.

18
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:34,760
You flatter me, Your Highness.

19
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:36,280
Who do you think you are?

20
00:01:36,760 --> 00:01:38,200
I wouldn't
waste my day thinking about you.

21
00:01:38,799 --> 00:01:40,359
Then why are you and Mu Ruyi here?

22
00:01:41,280 --> 00:01:43,159
Are you still
plotting to assassinate His Majesty?

23
00:01:44,519 --> 00:01:46,239
I don't care about Ling Xiao.

24
00:01:46,519 --> 00:01:48,120
I just want to find Ruyi!

25
00:01:50,319 --> 00:01:50,879
Wait,

26
00:01:52,239 --> 00:01:53,439
you mean that all this time,

27
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:54,599
Mu Ruyi,

28
00:01:55,079 --> 00:01:56,040
no, Liu Rushi

29
00:01:57,159 --> 00:01:58,799
has also been crazy
and trying to run away?

30
00:01:58,920 --> 00:02:01,239
We each serve our own masters
and protect their lives.

31
00:02:02,359 --> 00:02:03,640
You're the smart one, aren't you?

32
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:04,560
Go find your master then.

33
00:02:06,560 --> 00:02:07,400
Then, all this time,

34
00:02:07,959 --> 00:02:09,719
have you never thought of me even once?

35
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:13,639
I have.

36
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:17,280
I dream of you every single night.

37
00:02:17,879 --> 00:02:19,080
Every time I think of you,

38
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:20,919
I want to kill you.

39
00:02:21,879 --> 00:02:23,120
Once the Princess recovers,

40
00:02:24,520 --> 00:02:25,639
I'll settle all accounts with you,

41
00:02:26,319 --> 00:02:27,360
past and present.

42
00:02:29,560 --> 00:02:30,159
Fine.

43
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:32,080
I'll be waiting.

44
00:02:38,759 --> 00:02:39,840
Why did Xia Ke'er

45
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:41,159
run so fast?

46
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:43,479
Like she's charging into battle.

47
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:45,759
Miss,

48
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:46,919
alone?

49
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:49,159
Of course not.

50
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,719
My family is over there.

51
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:21,520
(I wish to hold your hand)

52
00:03:23,039 --> 00:03:24,159
(and grow old with you.)

53
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:26,439
(Since I met you,)

54
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:29,080
(every moment is so impressive.)

55
00:03:41,960 --> 00:03:44,159
Why would I dream about that eunuch?

56
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:45,919
But it seems so...

57
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,199
Look up and let me see.

58
00:03:58,199 --> 00:04:00,120
Just a normal girl.

59
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:02,879
One tael of silver, no more.

60
00:04:03,719 --> 00:04:05,479
I'm only worth one tael of silver?

61
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:07,080
How can you be a manager

62
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,360
with that kind of judgment?

63
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:10,879
I'll pay you two,

64
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:12,360
and you send me back.

65
00:04:13,159 --> 00:04:14,400
Who do you think you are

66
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:16,120
to make demands in my place?

67
00:04:16,319 --> 00:04:17,279
Your place?

68
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:18,720
Where do you work?

69
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:20,199
Say no more.

70
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:22,720
Just receive the guests from now on.

71
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:25,279
You'll make money someday.

72
00:04:25,279 --> 00:04:27,079
I'm just a burden.

73
00:04:27,079 --> 00:04:28,439
Those two idiots were lying to you.

74
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:32,800
What are you up to now?

75
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:33,920
To tell you the truth,

76
00:04:34,079 --> 00:04:36,319
though I'm beautiful,

77
00:04:36,560 --> 00:04:37,360
on my body,

78
00:04:37,519 --> 00:04:39,000
there's a huge scar

79
00:04:39,199 --> 00:04:41,160
from burns. It's terrible.

80
00:04:41,160 --> 00:04:43,439
Are you sure
your customers can take that?

81
00:04:45,680 --> 00:04:47,160
Mind take a closer look?

82
00:04:47,399 --> 00:04:49,600
Otherwise, your money would be wasted.

83
00:04:57,120 --> 00:04:58,079
You filthy wretch!

84
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:58,720
Get lost!

85
00:04:59,079 --> 00:05:00,319
Every time I see you, I'll beat you.

86
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:02,040
Eunuch, you're here!

87
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:04,519
One more word,

88
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:05,519
and I won't save you.

89
00:05:07,519 --> 00:05:08,920
How did you find me?

90
00:05:09,279 --> 00:05:10,720
They were suspicious,

91
00:05:10,839 --> 00:05:12,000
and they stole your purse.

92
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:13,720
After I treated you so badly,

93
00:05:13,879 --> 00:05:15,199
you still came to save me.

94
00:05:15,439 --> 00:05:15,920
Why?

95
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:17,360
I wanted to give you a proper lesson!

96
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:19,040
So let's just settle it outside!

97
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:23,079
However tough you act,

98
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:24,079
you're just a girl.

99
00:05:24,399 --> 00:05:26,360
It's dangerous
to act so rashly out here.

100
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:28,560
Where do you live? Let me take you home.

101
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:30,120
My home...

102
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:32,279
I don't even know
if that's really my home.

103
00:05:33,639 --> 00:05:35,319
Did you run away from home too?

104
00:05:35,439 --> 00:05:37,720
It's just me and a maid at home.

105
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:40,600
I stole her purse.

106
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:42,199
A maid?

107
00:05:42,879 --> 00:05:44,120
You must be quite wealthy.

108
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:45,680
I heard

109
00:05:46,079 --> 00:05:47,879
that my mother is in business.

110
00:05:48,319 --> 00:05:49,480
I came out alone

111
00:05:49,639 --> 00:05:51,639
just to find my only family member,

112
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:52,600
my mother.

113
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:54,000
You heard that?

114
00:05:54,639 --> 00:05:56,519
You're not familiar
with your family either?

115
00:05:56,680 --> 00:05:58,000
You still haven't told me

116
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:59,079
who you really are.

117
00:06:01,199 --> 00:06:01,800
Me?

118
00:06:02,399 --> 00:06:03,000
Just like you.

119
00:06:03,639 --> 00:06:04,439
Someone without a home,

120
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:06,040
who can't remember who he is.

121
00:06:07,319 --> 00:06:08,279
I see.

122
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:10,879
You sneaked away from your family

123
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:12,399
and ended up becoming a eunuch.

124
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:14,319
You must be unhappy about that.

125
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:15,920
You can't even do
what a normal man could,

126
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:18,279
like get married and have children.

127
00:06:18,519 --> 00:06:20,199
I'm not a eunuch!

128
00:06:20,759 --> 00:06:21,680
It's okay.

129
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:22,600
With me,

130
00:06:22,759 --> 00:06:24,199
you don't need to feel ashamed.

131
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:28,519
Let's just be brothers, well, sisters!

132
00:06:34,199 --> 00:06:34,879
You...

133
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:40,399
Keep your hands off.

134
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:41,720
I told you

135
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:43,639
I really am not a eunuch.

136
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:46,519
I'm sorry about that.

137
00:06:46,759 --> 00:06:47,639
My apologies.

138
00:06:48,319 --> 00:06:49,879
Looks like we're bound by fate.

139
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:52,879
Look at the beautiful sunset.

140
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:54,720
How about...

141
00:06:55,879 --> 00:06:56,399
How about?

142
00:06:57,079 --> 00:06:58,279
We're about the same age,

143
00:06:58,600 --> 00:06:59,600
we have similar experiences,

144
00:06:59,759 --> 00:07:01,879
and we started off so badly,

145
00:07:02,439 --> 00:07:05,079
just like a pair of bickering lovers
from storybooks.

146
00:07:05,519 --> 00:07:06,639
You saved me from danger

147
00:07:07,399 --> 00:07:08,399
this time,

148
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:10,720
I should...

149
00:07:11,079 --> 00:07:11,519
Miss,

150
00:07:11,879 --> 00:07:12,959
you don't need to
offer yourself in return.

151
00:07:13,399 --> 00:07:13,959
I saved you

152
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:15,800
simply because you have a kind face.

153
00:07:16,079 --> 00:07:17,360
You old fogey!

154
00:07:17,519 --> 00:07:18,800
Who said I'd give myself to you?

155
00:07:20,079 --> 00:07:21,600
Does anyone you save have to marry you?

156
00:07:22,079 --> 00:07:24,839
Then all the county officials

157
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:26,040
will have harems of their own!

158
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:29,680
Then how would you like to repay me?

159
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:32,480
I am considering it seriously,

160
00:07:32,959 --> 00:07:36,160
let's become sworn brothers.

161
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:38,519
I am Liu Rushi.

162
00:07:38,639 --> 00:07:40,319
May I have your name?

163
00:07:41,959 --> 00:07:42,720
I am Ling...

164
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:44,920
No, I am Mo Shuo.

165
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:47,120
"Mo" as in dark ink,
"Shuo" as in abundant.

166
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:48,519
Mo Shuo,

167
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:49,959
let's swear an oath.

168
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:51,040
Agree.

169
00:07:52,839 --> 00:07:54,000
Wait, not enough.

170
00:07:55,519 --> 00:07:55,920
Like this.

171
00:07:58,800 --> 00:08:00,319
This way, it'll be unforgettable.

172
00:08:00,759 --> 00:08:01,720
It doesn't make any sense.

173
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:04,439
But I suddenly feel fired up.

174
00:08:04,839 --> 00:08:07,560
From now on, we look out for each other.

175
00:08:07,879 --> 00:08:08,439
It's a deal.

176
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:09,480
It's a deal.

177
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:11,399
Brother!

178
00:08:11,519 --> 00:08:12,279
My brother!

179
00:08:13,199 --> 00:08:14,319
I'm so happy!

180
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:23,199
Liu Rushi!

181
00:08:24,959 --> 00:08:25,720
Where have you been?

182
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:26,920
You're driving me crazy!

183
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:28,040
Easy, easy...

184
00:08:28,199 --> 00:08:29,639
I just went to the market

185
00:08:29,839 --> 00:08:30,600
and cleared my head.

186
00:08:31,399 --> 00:08:32,919
Why are your clothes so dirty and messy?

187
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:34,639
Where have you been?

188
00:08:35,039 --> 00:08:36,320
It's a long story.

189
00:08:36,639 --> 00:08:37,360
How about I take a nap now

190
00:08:37,559 --> 00:08:38,399
and explain it later?

191
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:43,759
You're strong as an ox.

192
00:08:43,919 --> 00:08:45,399
It's a waste you're not
on the battlefield.

193
00:08:46,759 --> 00:08:47,960
Spill it out.

194
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:49,279
Don't mention it.

195
00:08:49,399 --> 00:08:51,080
Today was way too dangerous.

196
00:08:51,240 --> 00:08:52,120
I was knocked out

197
00:08:52,399 --> 00:08:54,279
and nearly sold off to a brothel.

198
00:08:54,919 --> 00:08:56,159
I tried my best

199
00:08:56,279 --> 00:08:57,080
to negotiate for a long time.

200
00:08:57,240 --> 00:08:58,559
In the end, a man saved me.

201
00:08:58,720 --> 00:09:00,200
The man drove the madam away

202
00:09:00,399 --> 00:09:02,279
and returned my stolen purse.

203
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:03,279
What man?

204
00:09:03,519 --> 00:09:04,799
He sounds very suspicious.

205
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:06,679
Anyone associated with a madam is

206
00:09:06,840 --> 00:09:07,639
surely no good.

207
00:09:07,799 --> 00:09:09,480
Don't speak of Mo Shuo that way!

208
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,120
How do you know Mo Shuo?

209
00:09:13,919 --> 00:09:16,639
Mo Shuo got involved
with a brothel madam?

210
00:09:17,279 --> 00:09:17,840
Yes.

211
00:09:18,039 --> 00:09:19,000
His name is Mo Shuo.

212
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:21,200
And we've become sworn brothers!

213
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:24,039
Mo Shuo!

214
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:25,679
Why are you so angry now?

215
00:09:25,879 --> 00:09:26,679
Are you on your period?

216
00:09:29,799 --> 00:09:30,600
Calm down!

217
00:09:30,799 --> 00:09:32,000
You don't need to avenge me!

218
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:33,039
Xia Ke'er!
